OL,6,FMoment undercover Met officers tackle
OL,7,Fphone thief to the ground in Oxford
OL,8,FCircus
OL,10,FDramatic video footage shows the
OL,11,Fmoment an undercover police officer
OL,12,Fstops a thief stealing a phone on one
OL,13,Fof London's busiest streets.
OL,15,FIn the video a man can be seen
OL,16,Ffollowing an unsuspecting tourist and
OL,17,Ftrying to remove a mobile phone from
OL,18,Fhis pocket in Oxford Circus.
