OL,3,CMoment Met officers tackle phone thief
OL,4,Cto the ground in Oxford Circus
OL,6,FSeconds later two plain clothes
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police officers, tackled
OL,8,Fhim to the ground.
OL,10,FOfficers noticed a man acting
OL,11,Fsuspiciously and paying attention to
OL,12,Fpeople's pockets and belongings. He
OL,13,Fwas then seen reaching towards the
OL,14,Fvictim and stealing his mobile phone,
OL,15,Fon Friday, 30 August.
OL,17,FOfficers arrested Sofian Hadar, 33, of
OL,18,FCricklewood Broadway, and returned the
OL,19,Fmobile phone to its owner - a heart
OL,20,Fsurgeon on holiday from Egypt.
