OL,3,CMoment Met officers tackle phone thief
OL,4,Cto the ground in Oxford Circus
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Hadar admitted to theft
OL,7,Fand was sentenced at Isleworth Crown
OL,8,FCourt to 11 months in prison.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Saj Hussain,
OL,11,Fwho leads on phone robbery and theft
OL,12,Fin the Met, said:
OL,14,F"Thanks to these observant and fast-
OL,15,Facting officers another mobile phone
OL,16,Fthief has been taken off the streets
OL,17,Fof London.
