OL,6,F"We understand the impact robbery can
OL,7,Fhave on victims and we also recognise
OL,8,Fthat there is still much more to do to
OL,9,Ftackle the problem as we make London
OL,10,Fsafer.
OL,12,F"Met officers are targeting resources
OL,13,Fin hotspot areas with increased
OL,14,Fpatrols and plain clothes officers -
OL,15,Fand this result makes clear this
OL,16,Fapproach is having a positive impact.
