OL,3,CMoment Met officers tackle phone thief
OL,4,Cto the ground in Oxford Circus
OL,6,FAs part of the A New Met for London
OL,7,Fplan, the Met is improving how we
OL,8,Fpolice more precisely, using
OL,9,Ftechnology and data to build
OL,10,Fintelligence and track stolen phones.
OL,11,FThis includes using 'Find my phone'
OL,12,Fdata to apprehend offenders and locate
OL,13,Fvictims' mobiles. This information is
OL,14,Fused to develop intelligence about
OL,15,Fcommon locations for where stolen
OL,16,Fphones are kept.
OL,18,FBetween January and June 2024 officers
OL,19,Fhave recovered more than 750 stolen
OL,20,Fphones.
